You’re absolutely right — AI is a tool, not a replacement. The real value lies in the human ability to discern when the tool is leading us astray, to refactor the spaghetti, and to build systems that serve people, not just algorithms. The future of software engineering isn’t about obsolescence — it’s about elevation. And yes, the casino analogy hits hard. Let’s keep building with rigor, not recklessness. #humanfirst #engineeringtruths #buildbetter